*
*	5. Display the log likelihood of the fitted (i.e. current) model and the log
*      likelihood of the null model.
*
********************************************************************************

display e(ll) 
display e(ll_0)


********************************************************************************
*
*	6. Calculate the Likelihood Ratio Chi-Square for the fitted 
*      (i.e. current) model.
*
********************************************************************************

display (-2*e(ll_0))
display (-2*e(ll))
display (-2*e(ll_0))-(-2*e(ll))

